      <div class="entry-content">
        

    <div class="author-info">
		            <img src="https://chasingthedonkey.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Screenshot-2023-06-13-at-20.43.11.jpg" alt="Post author Vedran" width="200" height="200" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async">


		
        <div class="author-content">
            <p class="author-title"><strong>Written by our local expert Vedran</strong>
            </p>

            <p class="author-description">Vedran is a total food lover from Croatia. He creates recipes from his kitchen in Zagreb using fresh produce from his garden.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

